p: Search result of previously published data set D1-D2 was downloaded from ProteomeXchange ( http://www.proteomexchange.org/) with identifier PXD006291 and PXD000279. Data set D4 was downloaded with identifier PXD004163. Data set D6 and D7 were downloaded with identifier PXD013276 and PXD005410. The data set D3 and D5 generated by us have been uploaded to ProteomeXchange accessed through identifier PXD013277 and PXD013276.
